(\BASEBYTES.NAME.FROM.STREAM
  [LAMBDA (STREAM)                                           (* ; "Edited 17-Jan-87 16:08 by bvm:")

    (* ;; "STRING streams have a FULLFILENAME which is just the string itself;  other random basebytes streams have this field null")

